data.description: 📍Eastside of Salisbury📍  Conveniently located to north RT 13 and the bypass and RT 50!  This 3 bedroom 2 bath rancher on a double lot  is waiting for you to call it home! This home has a unique floor plan with a surprise cabin like great room for warm cozy nights.  From the great room step out into the screened porch just waiting for a cookout or some steamed crabs, with a double lot with lots of room for a fire pit,  garden or a game of whiffle ball! Some stand outs are hardwood floors,  a laundry room with built in storage, fun little secret room upstairs, a practically brand new bathroom with a walk in shower and a  particle basement. Lots of fun family memories have been made in this home, you can make more too!  Home has  recently had a water test and termite test completed.  Located close to the bypass,  restaurants and shopping on the Eastside of town.  Home is being sold " AS-IS' .  Don't miss out on this opportunity.
